'''Goblins''' are a common [[monster]] for new players to train on. There are many wandering around in [[Lumbridge]], where players start, so they are commonly one of the first monsters players will ever kill. They are great monsters to train on because they are weak, making them easy to kill. Although these monsters are great to train on and gain profit from at lower levels, not many players kill them.

== Locations==
===Level 7===
*Around [[Lumbridge]]
*East [[Draynor]] (only 1 in Wheat Field)
*West of [[Port Sarim Jail]]
*[[Goblin Cave]] near the [[Fishing Guild]]
===Level 13===
*Just west of [[Varrock]]
*[[Goblin Village]]
*Around [[Taverley]]
*Northwest of [[Ardougne]]
*[[Goblin Cave]] near the [[Fishing Guild]]
*[[Tree Gnome Village]]
*[[Observatory dungeon]] and a goblin settlement northeast of [[Observatory]]

===Level 19===
*[[Observatory dungeon]]

