====Notes====

* [[Goblin armour]] and [[bronze spear]]s are dropped at the same time.
* About 12% of runes dropped are [[earth rune]]s, 35% are [[water rune]]s, and the rest are [[body rune]]s.
* Water runes and [[crossbow bolt]]s are dropped at around the same rate as each other.
* However, body runes are only dropped at around 13% of the rate of coins.
* [[Chef's hat]]s are dropped at 13% of the rate of earth runes.



